title: #127: Parapsychology and Remote Viewing with Brent Weinbach
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another crazy ass episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode Sam welcome hilarious comic and clairvoyant, Brent Weinbach, to discuss the world of parapsychology.
1) His special "Appealing to the Main Stream."
2) Remote Viewing
3) Clairvoyance
4) ESP and Psychic ability
5) MK Ultra
6) The Voice Of God
7) Smart Phones reading your mind.
Thank you so much for listening and supporting the show.
